{
  "texts": [
    "As displayed in Fig. 1, different from the recent summary for battery informatics [1] [2] [3] [4] [5], we will summarize progress and current challenges in applying ML and computation tools for battery research from an application-oriented perspective.",
    "In the end, we also propose potential research frontiers to further improve the field.",
    "The comprehensive understanding of ML on these challenges is insightful and will further promote the integration of ML in battery science.",
    "As the core of AI, ML technology is of great significance to human life and technological advancement [6] [7] [8] [9].",
    "Coupling ML with battery research will reduce the experimental cost of discovering the next generation of advanced batteries."
  ]
}